--- ./tests/test_branches.py
+++ ./tests/test_branches.py
@@ -6,6 +6,10 @@
 
 
 @given(locations, locations)
+@example(
+    start=Location(filename="", line=0, column=None),
+    end=Location(filename="", line=0, column=None),
+).via("HypoFuzz covering example")

     branch = Branch.make(start, end)
     assert branch.start == start
@@ -13,6 +17,10 @@

+    start=Location(filename="", line=0, column=None),
+    end=Location(filename="", line=0, column=None),
